show.description: Kya hota hai jab ek common girl ban jati hai duniya ke sabse ameer aadmi ki biwi vo bhi sirf ek deal ke liye? Par jab dil sach bolne lage, to badal jata hai game. Romance aur drama se bhara ye show aapko emotional rollercoaster pe le jayega. Abhi dekhna shuru kijiye.
